--------------------------- 

* bug fixes for gdfnotebook. (Thanks Rune)

* fix to make dnd work as expected with gedit.

* bug fixes for gtoolbar, gmenu when icons were involved. Issue arose
with newer GTK versions. (Thanks Rune)

